---
// splash screen - click anywhere to enter the site
---

<div class="splash-overlay" id="splash-overlay">
  <div class="splash-card">
    <div class="splash-image">
      <img src="/images/tree-geometric.png" alt="" />
    </div>

    <h2 class="splash-title">On Ignorance as Remedy</h2>

    <div class="splash-text">
      <p>Struck by the happiness of this poor creature, I returned to my philosopher.</p>
      <p>"Are you not ashamed," I said, "to be thus miserable—when not fifty yards from you an old laborer sits content, thinking of nothing?"</p>
      <p>He turned his face toward the window, toward that distant figure.</p>
      <p>"You are right," he said. "I have told myself a thousand times: I should be happy, were I but as ignorant as my neighbor."</p>
      <p>He paused.</p>
      <p>The afternoon light fell slant across his books, his instruments, his unanswered letters.</p>
      <p class="splash-final">"—it is a happiness I do not desire."</p>
    </div>

    <span class="splash-hint">click to enter</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  .splash-overlay {
    position: fixed !important;
    top: 0 !important;
    left: 0 !important;
    right: 0 !important;
    bottom: 0 !important;
    z-index: 99999 !important;
    background: var(--bg-start);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* melt away animation */
  .splash-overlay.melting {
    animation: melt 800ms ease-out forwards;
  }

  @keyframes melt {
    0% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      filter: blur(8px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
  }

  .splash-card {
    background: var(--bg-paper);
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
    padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .splash-image {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .splash-image img {
    max-width: 140px;
    height: auto;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .splash-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .splash-text {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-soft);
  }

  .splash-text p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .splash-final {
    color: var(--accent-warm) !important;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-top: 1rem !important;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  .splash-hint {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-cool);
    opacity: 0.7;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { opacity: 0.9; }
  }

  /* hide body scroll when splash is visible */
  body:has(.splash-overlay:not(.melting)) {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .splash-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
    }

    .splash-image img {
      max-width: 100px;
    }

    .splash-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .splash-title {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  (function() {
    var splash = document.getElementById('splash-overlay');
    if (!splash) return;

    function closeSplash() {
      splash.classList.add('melting');
      setTimeout(function() {
        splash.remove();
      }, 800);
    }

    splash.addEventListener('click', closeSplash);
  })();
</script>
